            <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;hey-im-robin-&#34;&gt;Hey, I&amp;rsquo;m Robin 👋&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Builder, photographer, and lifelong tinkerer.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I spend my days building products at the intersection of technology and creativity. This site is where I share what I&amp;rsquo;m learning, what I&amp;rsquo;m building, and what I&amp;rsquo;m seeing through my lens.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-youll-find-here&#34;&gt;What You&amp;rsquo;ll Find Here&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;📝 &lt;strong&gt;Blog&lt;/strong&gt; — Deep dives into tech, AI, cloud architecture, and the occasional hot take.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;🛠 &lt;strong&gt;Projects&lt;/strong&gt; — Things I&amp;rsquo;ve built, from side projects to serious products.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;📷 &lt;strong&gt;Photography&lt;/strong&gt; — Moments captured. Mostly street, travel, and architecture.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;get-in-touch&#34;&gt;Get in Touch&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Feel free to reach out via &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://linkedin.com/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;</description>
